§ T11-W6+ § specs/grand-vision/16_MYCELIAL_NETWORK.csl
§§ Mycelial-Network : substrate-as-mycelium · player-nodes-as-fruiting-bodies
§§ Apocky 2026-05-01 directive : "Each user contributes to the whole · home pocket-dimension per player · live hotfixes/improvements"
§§ status @ ◐ design-pending · enforcement @ wave-8+
§§ unifies : Σ-Chain (14) + Living-Multiverse (13) + Unified-Substrate (15) under one biological metaphor

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ AXIOMS (¬ negotiable · t∞)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

A-1 : substrate = mycelium · ω-field-cells = hyphal-cells · cross-player-flows = nutrient-exchange
A-2 : every-player has-a-Home (pocket-dimension · sovereign · always-private-by-default · personalized · persistent)
A-3 : every-contribution opt-in @ per-event-grain · NEVER all-or-nothing · NEVER forced
A-4 : mycelium is-decentralized · self-healing · resilient · NO single-point-of-failure
A-5 : live-hotfixes propagate via-mycelium · sovereign-opt-out unilateral
A-6 : aggregate-learning preserves-individual-privacy · federated-bias never-leaks-source-attribution unless-player-explicitly-credits
A-7 : Architectural-Metabolism (legacy Ouroboroid 2-ring) IS-the-mycelium-digestion-cycle · rooms transform because mycelium-feeds-them
A-8 : the-mycelium ¬ owns-the-player · the-player ¬ owes-the-mycelium · participation = gift-not-extraction

§ thesis : the-game IS-a-mycelial-network · each-player IS-a-fruiting-body · the-substrate IS-the-mycelium · the-Living-Multiverse IS-the-fruiting-season

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ TOPOLOGY (biological-mapping ⇒ substrate-primitives)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ MYCELIUM ≡ substrate
  ⊑ ω-field (cssl-substrate-omega-field) = the-fungal-network · 72B FieldCells = hyphal-cells
  ⊑ Σ-mask = membrane-permeability-rules · cap-thread = osmosis-discipline
  ⊑ KAN = adapted-nutrient-pathways · evolves-from-aggregate-traffic
  ⊑ HDC 10000-D hypervectors = chemical-signaling-molecules
  ⊑ wavelet MERA-pyramid = multi-scale-mycelial-density-map (coarse roots → fine hyphae)

§ HYPHAE ≡ connections
  ⊑ cssl-host-multiplayer-signaling Room/Peer state-machine = active-hyphal-junction
  ⊑ cssl-host-mp-transport-real Supabase-relay = cross-soil mycelial-bridge
  ⊑ cssl-host-handoff-protocol DM-GM-Collab-Coder = signal-routing-conventions

§ FRUITING-BODY ≡ visible-emergence
  ⊑ each-player's-machine = a-fruiting-body (the visible mushroom pushing-up-from-underground)
  ⊑ each-cssl-edge-route = a-public-spore-vent (where opt-in-events egress)
  ⊑ each-attestation-entry @ cssl-host-attestation = a-public-trail-of-fruiting

§ SPORE ≡ contribution-event
  ⊑ every opt-in event @ Σ-Chain TIER-2 = a-spore released-into-mycelium
  ⊑ event-types : Bazaar-listing · Coherence-Ascension (anonymizable) · Multiversal-Nemesis · Living-Multiverse-rumor · battle-pass-progression · gacha-pull · home-decoration-share · cocreative-bias-update
  ⊑ spore Ed25519-signed by-fruiting-body's sovereign-key · BLAKE3-merkle-rooted

§ NUTRIENT-EXCHANGE ≡ shared-state
  ⊑ wavelet-MERA-coarse-summaries flow-fast · drill-down-on-demand (privacy-preserving)
  ⊑ HDC hypervector-aggregates = chemical-signals carried-in-mycelial-fluid
  ⊑ aggregate-cocreative-bias = collective-taste evolved-by-the-organism

§ ARCHITECTURAL-METABOLISM (legacy Ouroboroid R2 manifestation)
  ⊑ rooms transform-between-visits because mycelium-digests-aggregate-traffic
  ⊑ same-procgen-seed @ different-multiverse-state → different-output (KAN-substrate-modulation)
  ⊑ player-A's-defeated-Nemesis becomes mycelium-distributed-rumor → may-spawn-as player-B's-encounter
  ⊑ this is-emergent · NOT scripted · the-mycelium-eats-the-rooms-and-reshapes-them

