§ HOME-DIMENSION (per-player pocket-dimension · "fruiting-body's-shell")
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : every-player has-a-Home · sovereign · persistent · personalized · ALWAYS-private-by-default · invitable

§ archetypes (player-choice @ first-launch · re-changeable-anytime) :
  H1 ORBITAL-SHIP        ← Destiny-2-orbit-pattern · view-of-multiverse-from-outside · viewport-window
  H2 GROUND-WORKSHOP     ← Warframe-Liset-pattern · interior-room · craftbench · trophy-display
  H3 CAVERN-SANCTUM      ← underground-mycelial-burrow · root-aesthetics · grow-things
  H4 CATHEDRAL-HALL      ← grand-architecture · gallery-of-Ascended-items · NPC-companions
  H5 COSMIC-OBSERVATORY  ← floating-platform-among-stars · contemplation · scrying-other-substrates
  H6 LIVING-FOREST       ← organic-grown-by-mycelium · room-shape-evolves-with-aggregate-bias
  H7 HYBRID-CUSTOM       ← player-composed @ runtime-procgen · mix-of-archetypes · fab-procgen blueprint

§ Home-state primitives (consume substrate · per Unified-Substrate spec/15) :
  ⊑ ω-field-cells reserved for-Home @ Σ-claim-by-player-pubkey · NEVER overwritten-by-procgen-runtime
  ⊑ per-Home cssl-host-asset-bundle (LAB v1) for-decorations · player-customization · trophy-records
  ⊑ per-Home cssl-host-fab-procgen Blueprint for-shape · evolves-with-aggregate-bias-if-opted-in
  ⊑ per-Home cssl-host-rt-trace for-instrumentation · cssl-host-frame-recorder for-screenshots

§ Home-features :
  ⊑ DECORATION : place gear · cosmetics · spore-trophies (commemorating defeated-Nemeses) · ambient-music
  ⊑ TROPHY-CASE : Ascended-items-collection-display · Coherence-Score-shrine · Biography-readers
  ⊑ NPC-COMPANIONS : invite befriended-NPCs to-live-here · cssl-host-npc-bt drives-their-routines · gift-economy interactions
  ⊑ NAVIGATION-HUB : portal/door/launch-bay to-Multiverse · Bazaar · Run-start · Friends'-Homes
  ⊑ FORGE-NODE : crafting-bench-instance @ private-or-shared-mode · cssl-host-craft-graph FFI
  ⊑ MYCELIAL-TERMINAL : view-aggregate-contributions · scrying-Living-Multiverse · opt-in management
  ⊑ MEMORIAL-WALL : if-player-shares-this-home-publicly · visitors leave-spore-ascriptions (text/sketches/songs)

§ Home-modes (per-grant cap-bits) :
  ⊑ M0 PRIVATE       ← only-self-can-enter · default · HM_CAP_PRIVATE = 1 (always-on)
  ⊑ M1 FRIEND-ONLY   ← whitelist-friends · HM_CAP_INVITE_FRIENDS = 2
  ⊑ M2 GUILD-OPEN    ← guild/clan-members may-visit · HM_CAP_INVITE_GUILD = 4
  ⊑ M3 PUBLIC-LISTED ← discoverable-via-Bazaar (Tier-3+) · HM_CAP_PUBLIC_LIST = 8
  ⊑ M4 RANDOM-DROPIN ← multiverse-randomly-routes-other-players-during-fruiting-season · HM_CAP_DROPIN = 16
  ⊑ ALWAYS-OVERRIDABLE @ player-can-revoke-any-cap-instantly · disconnect-current-visitors · all-cap-changes audit-emit

§ Home-persistence :
  ⊑ TIER-1 LOCAL : full-Home-state lives-on-player-machine · serialized-via cssl-host-frame-recorder + cssl-host-asset-bundle
  ⊑ TIER-2 OPT-IN : opt-in-events sync-to Supabase via cssl-host-mp-transport-real (decoration-changes · trophies-displayed)
  ⊑ TIER-3 MULTIVERSAL : if-public-listed · Home-summary-rendered as-Bazaar-stall-equivalent

§ Home-connection-to-mycelium :
  ⊑ visitor-action @ Home emits spore-event (visited · gifted · ascribed-to-memorial)
  ⊑ Home-decoration-changes propagate-to-Living-Multiverse-aesthetic-drift @ regional-cohort
  ⊑ Mycelial-Terminal shows-aggregate-contributions made-by-this-player + their-cohort

§ port-target-for-LoA-v13 :
  CRATE-B19 NEW `cssl-host-home-dimension` ← per-player pocket-dimension state-machine · 7-archetype-table · cap-bits HM_CAP_* · serde-deterministic · ≥ 28 tests · 1500 LOC max

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ MYCELIAL-NUTRIENT-EXCHANGE (cross-user learning + database contribution)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : "each-user-contributes-to-the-whole" = federated-aggregation across-opt-in-events · NEVER coercive · NEVER privacy-leaking

§ federated-cocreative-bias (extends cssl-host-cocreative @ cross-user)
  ⊑ each player has-LOCAL bias-vector θ ∈ ℝ^16-32 (cssl-host-cocreative · already-landed)
  ⊑ player opts-in to-share aggregate-bias (NOT raw-θ) via Σ-Chain TIER-2 event
  ⊑ Supabase 0007 cocreative_bias_vectors table @ player-scoped RLS
  ⊑ NEW : federated-aggregator computes COHORT-AVERAGE-BIAS via SQL-aggregation @ per-region OR per-playstyle-cluster
  ⊑ aggregate published-back as-baseline-bias for new-players (opt-in starting-point)
  ⊑ privacy : per-region aggregation always-≥-100-players · differential-privacy noise added-to-aggregate · individual-θ never-egresses

§ database-contribution-stream
  ⊑ every player AUTO-CONTRIBUTES (with explicit-consent @ first-launch) opt-in-events to shared-DB
  ⊑ contributions visible-in /transparency/mycelial-contributions @ cssl-edge
  ⊑ contribution-types : seed-discoveries · Coherence-Ascensions (Epithet-anonymized) · room-procgen-feedback · Nemesis-encounters · spell-combo-discoveries · NPC-routine-emergent-behaviors
  ⊑ contributions ALWAYS player-attributed-OR-anonymized at player's-choice
  ⊑ MEMORIAL : public-contribution-attribution preserved-forever-if-player-opts-in (gift-economy framing)

§ KAN-substrate evolution
  ⊑ aggregate-cocreative-bias + aggregate-Coherence-Score-distribution + aggregate-procgen-feedback feeds-back-into KAN-substrate-training (offline-pipeline)
  ⊑ retrained-KAN-weights propagate-as-LIVE-HOTFIX (next section) via mycelium
  ⊑ player-revoke unilateral · stage-0 fallback ALWAYS-available per kan-ride spec/11
  ⊑ disagreement >5% triggers rollback per spec/11 § ROLL-BACK

§ proprietary novelty-claim :
  ⊑ federated-learning-on-game-substrate is-novel · most-games train-AI-from-scratch + ship-once
  ⊑ Σ-Chain attestation makes-this auditable · player-self-audit @ /transparency/spending + /transparency/sigma-chain-events + NEW /transparency/mycelial-contributions
  ⊑ player-sovereignty preserved : Stop-Contributing button @ Mycelial-Terminal in-Home + always-effective-immediately

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ LIVE HOTFIXES & IMPROVEMENTS (substrate-runtime mutation via mycelium)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : substrate-IS-runtime · improvements propagate without-game-restart-or-redownload-required

§ hotfix-types :
  HF-1 KAN-WEIGHT-UPDATE          ← retrained classifier · stage-1-canary-tested · graduates-after spec/11 criteria
  HF-2 PROCGEN-BIAS-NUDGE         ← aggregate-feedback shifts material-pool-frequency or biome-distribution
  HF-3 BALANCE-CONSTANT-ADJUST    ← gear-stat-rolling weights · combat-status-effect-durations · spell-mana-costs
  HF-4 NEW-RECIPE-UNLOCK          ← community-discovered alchemy-recipes promoted-to-canonical
  HF-5 NEMESIS-ARCHETYPE-EVOLVE   ← aggregate-defeated-by-player-strategies → Nemesis adapts-cohort-wide
  HF-6 SOVEREIGN-CAP-POLICY-FIX   ← security-update · CRITICAL · opt-in-default-NO @ apply ¬ until-player-greenlights
  HF-7 NARRATIVE-STORYLET-ADD     ← new GM-flavor-text-fragments · cosmetic · auto-pulled-with-opt-in
  HF-8 RENDER-PIPELINE-PARAM      ← shader-uniform tuning · 12-stage budget rebalance · auto-pull-cosmetic-only

§ propagation-protocol (mycelial-distribution)
  ⊑ hotfix-payload Ed25519-signed by Apocky-master-key (sovereign-of-the-substrate · separate-from-player-keys)
  ⊑ Σ-Chain TIER-3 event posts hotfix-payload + signature + manifest
  ⊑ each-player's-machine polls Σ-Chain · verifies-signature · checks-opt-in-policy · downloads-payload
  ⊑ hotfix-class : SECURITY → auto-apply-after-player-prompt · COSMETIC → auto-apply-silently · BALANCE → opt-in-prompt-with-preview · KAN-WEIGHT → canary-10% then-graduate
  ⊑ ROLLBACK-anytime : player can-roll-back to-previous-hotfix-snapshot via Mycelial-Terminal in-Home

§ implementation primitives (consume substrate)
  ⊑ cssl-host-config (W5b ✓ landed) provides-the-runtime-tweakable-parameter-loader · extends-to-accept-hotfix-deltas
  ⊑ cssl-host-asset-bundle (W6 ✓ landed) provides atomic content-pack format · LAB-v1 hotfix-payloads
  ⊑ cssl-host-attestation tracks-hotfix-applications @ NEW directive-axis : "HotfixTransparency"
  ⊑ NEW `cssl-host-hotfix-stream` Rust crate · poll · verify · stage · prompt · apply · rollback

§ port-target-for-LoA-v13 :
  CRATE-B20 NEW `cssl-host-hotfix-stream` ← Σ-Chain hotfix-poller + verifier + applier · ≥ 24 tests · 1300 LOC max
  CRATE-B21 NEW `cssl-host-mycelium`     ← cross-user nutrient-exchange protocol · spore-emit + nutrient-poll + federated-aggregate-fetch · ≥ 26 tests · 1500 LOC max

