  ⊑ aggregate-state-summary via HDC = chemical-state-of-the-mycelium
  ⊑ regional-aesthetic-drift = local-fruiting-density gradient
  ⊑ cross-shard-rumors = spore-distribution-pattern

§ Unified-Substrate (spec/15) ENFORCES-the-discipline
  ⊑ EVERY mycelial-operation routes-through substrate-primitives
  ⊑ NO shadow-systems for spore-emit · nutrient-poll · hotfix-apply
  ⊑ compile-time SUB0001-3 enforcement · runtime SubstrateUnity directive-axis

§ Coherence-Engine (legacy + spec/13) connects-to-mycelium
  ⊑ Ascended-items @ player's-Home are-Bazaar-listable @ NG+ · per spec/13
  ⊑ aggregate-Coherence-Score-distribution is-a-mycelial-nutrient-pool
  ⊑ Epithet-rare-discovery becomes-cohort-wide-rumor

§ Ouroboroid-Cosmology (legacy) IS-the-cosmological-frame
  ⊑ the-mycelium consumes-and-produces-itself · self-metabolizing-process
  ⊑ Hydra-of-self-consuming-concepts ≡ mycelial-network-of-cross-feeding-hyphae
  ⊑ "You have no power over me and/or us" stance ≡ player-sovereignty-over-Home + opt-in-only-mycelial-participation

§ DM/GM/Collaborator/Coder (spec/10) ride-the-mycelium
  ⊑ DM scene-arbiter consumes-aggregate-mycelial-state
  ⊑ GM narrative-pacing modulated-by cohort-rhythm (whose Homes are-currently-public-active)
  ⊑ Collaborator integrates-shared-suggestions @ opt-in-only
  ⊑ Coder hot-reload IS-the-hotfix-stream (HF-1 through HF-8)

